# Convert CJK characters
# Note: adds space between them and letters.
:: (halfwidth-fullwidth);
:: (katakana-latin);
:: (hiragana-latin);

$terminalPunct = [\.\,\:\;\?\!．，：？！。、；[:Pe:][:Pf:]];
$terminalPunct { } [:L:] > ' ';
[:L:] { } [[:Han:][:Ps:][:Pi:]]> ' ';

$kata = [[ﾞﾟｰー][:katakana:]];
$kata { } [[:L:]-$kata]> ' ';
[[:L:]-$kata] { } $kata > ' ';

[:hiragana:] { } [[:L:]-[:hiragana:]] > ' ';
[[:L:]-[:hiragana:]] { } [:hiragana:]> ' ';
